Editor Settings
Press PF4 in the editor to open the settings screen.
Settings are saved per user and persist across sessions.

AUTOINSERT   ON/OFF   When ON, pressing Enter on the last line
                      inserts a new blank line.  Default: ON.

VERBOSE      ON/OFF   When ON, informational messages are shown
                      in the message line (e.g. "2 lines deleted").
                      Error messages are always shown.  Default: ON.

Change a value and press Enter to save.  PF3 cancels.

See also: {keys:Function Keys}
